    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in showroom condition. This one-owner masterpiece has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its original factory luster. The exterior paint is deep and reflective, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body line is crisp, and the wheels remain in flawless condition without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather remains supple and taut, smelling as fresh as the day it left the assembly line. All technological features, including the high-resolution infotainment and driver-assist systems, operate with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of dealership service records and a pristine engine bay. This is a rare opportunity to own an investment-grade example that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new car.",
      "price": 48900.0,
